item.title: Deloitte relocates 5,000 staff to new sustainable offices in Southwark
item.description: Deloitte has completed the move into a 350,000 sq ft workspace on Bankside, consolidating five London offices into one net-zero headquarters.

item.title: Ed Sheeran announces surprise acoustic tour of UK cathedrals
item.description: The singer-songwriter will perform intimate sets in historic venues across the country this winter.

item.title: Landsec launches new flexible office brand targeting SMEs in the West End
item.description: Landsec has unveiled a new 120,000 sq ft co-working concept offering short leases and fully serviced workspaces.

item.title: British Airways adds new route between London City and Geneva
item.description: The new flight service will operate twice daily to meet demand from business travellers and skiers.

item.title: Amazon signs long-term lease for 300,000 sq ft logistics hub in Milton Keynes
item.description: The new fulfilment centre will create over 1,500 jobs and serve as Amazon’s regional distribution base.

item.title: London Marathon 2026 charity ballot opens for entries
item.description: Runners can now apply for one of 15,000 fundraising places ahead of next year’s race.

item.title: GPE secures planning consent for new 250,000 sq ft office tower near Tottenham Court Road
item.description: Great Portland Estates will redevelop the former retail block into a mixed-use building featuring premium office floors and rooftop terraces.

item.title: BBC announces cast for new drama series set in post-war London
item.description: The six-part historical drama begins filming this month and will air on BBC One in 2026.

item.title: BT Group consolidates regional teams into new digital campus in Bristol
item.description: BT’s new 180,000 sq ft facility will host engineers and software developers relocated from Reading and Swindon offices.

item.title: Taylor Swift breaks UK streaming records with latest album release
item.description: The new album became the most streamed release in a single day on Spotify UK.
